text:
Sorry, I'm kinda still lost in my thoughts. 
 I feel like I just made a lifelong friend… another one, anyways.

Seriously though, thank you for everything. 
 It means so much to me to have such good people in my life.

Well, back on topic, it's renovation time, right? 
 I can't imagine feeling much better than this, 
 but I'm curious what you'll come up with. Good luck!
